		<div class="lia-message-body-content">
			
                
                    I thought that all the places of each "World" were one planet (Crux) Also, NT is on the same place as CP. AND CP is a barren canyon-world with oceans of maelstrom, and the only "Cities" there are are Point zeta and the monastery ruins.<BR /><BR />Sorry if I sound rude right now. Just wanted to correct something.
                
            
			
				
			
			
